{"tid":1539902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解呢個地方從來無人講過？","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:27:09.000Z","uid":267838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c049cbf96f913970b3281f64519e30aacdde7cb9","tid":1539902,"uid":267838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong>代友post</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n有個地方仲安全過機場，但從來無人講過!<br />\n<br />\n成座大家成日都望到，成條塞米咁點解咁耐都無人講過？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">IFC 1 有<strong>新鴻基地產</strong><br />\nIFC 2 有 <strong>HKMA</strong><br />\n兩橦都有<strong>勁多中資，仲有一堆律師樓，iBank</strong><br />\n每個辦公室單日租金以萬計</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲未計<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">IFC mall</span></strong><br />\n入面最出名嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Apple Store, City&rsquo;super同 Lane Crawford</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">單單LC一日營業額已經過百萬計<br />\n成個商場一日營業額都過千萬計</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有下面就係機場快線<br />\n隔離<strong>交易廣場有 SFC 同 HKEx仲有四叔間四季</strong><br />\n<br />\nPopo 冇可能放催淚彈<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期一至五 9am to 4pm 交易時段亦都唔會敢出防暴</span></span><br />\n<br />\n參照「和你飛」接機活動，我地可以係 IFC 2 在商場內的𨋢口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1JB3Yb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1JB3Yb2.jpg&h=7919b245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接放 lunch，舉牌，和和平平咁，對象係遊客同 expat。𨋢囗外可坐面積媲美機場 T1，交通方便過機場好多。<br />\n<br />\n係商場到唔太同意癱瘓或有阻塞，宣傳對象係外媒，唔好俾到位人去清場。<br />\n<br />\nRent reference <br />\n$92,000 per day for HNA<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/property/hong-kong-china/article/2062032/hna-group-expands-its-hong-kong-headquarters-two-ifc-hk276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fproperty%2Fhong-kong-china%2Farticle%2F2062032%2Fhna-group-expands-its-hong-kong-headquarters-two-ifc-hk276&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcah3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=70baf59f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/property/hong-kong-china/article/2062032/hna-group-expands-its-hong-kong-headquarters-two-ifc-hk276</a>"},{"pid":"e13b1d73e234c3800d38e564b5945e5a74d7bec2","tid":1539902,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:32:51.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a739d96f56fbbc8516eb0bfe73e3476f198676","tid":1539902,"uid":267838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"自推 10"},{"pid":"a3130927be59508c6140dbb80cb5a36ab9d2cf68","tid":1539902,"uid":267838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:48:32.000Z","msg":"自推 9"},{"pid":"b53ea6b09c51b2f8a7edfb0899bec5e0d5617ffb","tid":1539902,"uid":267838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"自推 8"},{"pid":"78ba10113c7e0e066f1a5c134e50f76edfaf630c","tid":1539902,"uid":267838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"fbc05297c602e5146c7b34947e3e664e9c90c4dd","tid":1539902,"uid":267838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:51:05.000Z","msg":"自推 6"},{"pid":"4b6c959d29a638be2064748af52f766b9dafaa64","tid":1539902,"uid":267838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"自推 5"},{"pid":"d588201920